                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-646-18350202 t18350202-646-punishment-133"></join>Confined Three Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Second Jury, before Mr. Recorder</hi>.</p>
